# Asset meta data should only be ignored when the temp cache is the only place they exist
# (handled by Unity automatically); keep .meta for tracked assets.

# Visual Studio / Rider / VS Code cache
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/

# Unity-generated solution & project files
